isability from a suitably qualified professional. </p>\n\n<p>You can get up to:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>£20,520 for a helper</li>\n  <li>£5,162 for specialist equipment for the whole course</li>\n  <li>£1,724 for other costs</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Practice placement expenses</h3>\n\n<p>If you do a practice placement you may be able to claim travel costs if:  </p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>your practice placement is in a hospital or community health centre and not at your university</li>\n  <li>it costs you more to travel to your placement than it costs to travel to university</li>\n</ul>\n"}]},"tags":[{"title":"Student finance, loans and universities","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/education%2Fstudent-finance.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Including loans, bursaries, grants, student finance and paying back loans","short_description":"","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=education%2Fstudent-finance","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/education/student-finance"},"parent":{"title":"Education and learning","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/education.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Get help if you&#39;re at school, planning to go on to further or higher education, looking for training or interested in a student or career development loan.","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=education","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/education"},"parent":null}}],"related":[{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/extra-money-pay-university.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/extra-money-pay-university","title":"Extra money to pay for university","format":"answer","updated_at":"2013-01-09T13:12:12+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/social-work-bursaries.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/social-work-bursaries","title":"Social work bursaries","format":"programme","updated_at":"2013-01-09T13:12:35+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/student-finance-calc