y for a Tuition Fee Loan, Maintenance Loan and Maintenance Grant. </p>\n\n<p>Part-time students can apply for Tuition Fee Grant and Course Grant. </p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"European Union\">EU</abbr> full-time students can apply for a Tuition Fee Loan. <abbr title=\"European Union\">EU</abbr> part-time students can apply for a Tuition Fee Grant.</p>\n\n<h2>Apply for student finance</h2>\n\n<p>You have to apply every year. You need your passport details the first time you apply. Don&rsquo;t send your UK passport.</p>\n\n<p>Only <abbr title=\"European Union\">EU</abbr> students have to send their passport or identity card.  </p>\n\n<p>You can apply up to 9 months after the start of your course.</p>\n\n<p>About 6 weeks after your online application you&rsquo;ll get a declaration form in the post. Sign this and send it back. </p>\n\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Student</th>\n      <th>Application forms (2011 to 2012 academic year)</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>UK full-time students</td>\n      <td><a href=\"/student-finance-register-login\" title=\"Apply online for student finance\">Apply online</a></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>UK part-time students</td>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/documents/digitalasset/dg_199087.pdf\" title=\"part-time students (PDF, 402KB)\">Part-time student application (PDF, 402KB)</a> <br /> <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/@educ/documents/digitalasset/dg_199977.pdf\" title=\"part-time student income confirmation form  (PDF, 89KB)\">Income confirmation form (PDF, 89KB)</a> <br /> <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/@educ/documents/digitalasset/dg_199975.pdf\" title=\"part-time student benefits confirmation form (PDF, 265KB)\">Benefits confirmation form (PDF, 265KB)</a> <br /> <a rel=\"external\